              </svg>
              GitHub
            </a>
            <a href="/projects/inclusive-starter" class="link-docs">
              Dokumentaatio
              <span class="coming-soon-text">(tulossa)</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Studies -->
    <section class="case-studies-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Case Studies</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          Tulossa: Syvällisiä analyysejä julkisista palveluista ja konkreettisia 
          ratkaisuja saavutettavuusongelmiin.
        </p>
        
        <div class="case-grid">
          <div class="case-card">
            <div class="case-number">01</div>
            <h3>Julkisten palveluiden saavutettavuus</h3>
            <p>
              Miten voimme tehdä kriittisistä palveluista helpompia käyttää 
              silloin kun elämä on hektistä?
            </p>
            <span class="status-badge status-planned">Suunnitteilla</span>
          </div>

          <div class="case-card">
            <div class="case-number">02</div>
            <h3>Komponentteja jotka toimivat stressitilanteissa</h3>
            <p>
              Saavutettavuus ei ole lisäominaisuus vaan lähtökohta.
            </p>
            <span class="status-badge status-planned">Suunnitteilla</span>
          </div>

          <div class="case-card">
            <div class="case-number">03</div>
            <h3>Saavutettavuus käytännössä</h3>
            <p>
              Miten suunnitellaan oikeille ihmisille oikeissa tilanteissa ensimmäisestä versiosta lähtien?
            </p>
            <span class="status-badge status-planned">Suunnitteilla</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Kiinnostuitko?</h2>
          <p>
            Ota yhteyttä jos haluat keskustella saavutettavuudesta, 
            tarvitset apua projektissasi, tai haluat vain vaihtaa ajatuksia.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:maiju@altmaian.dev" class="cta-button">
            Ota yhteyttä →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ============================================
     CSS Variables
     ============================================ */
  :root {
    --color-bg: #0a0a0f;
    --color-bg-secondary: #13131a;
    --color-text: #e8e8ee;
    --color-text-muted: #9d9daa;
    --color-accent-turquoise: #06d6a0;
    --color-accent-purple: #a855f7;
    --spacing-sm: 1rem;
    --spacing-md: 2rem;
    --spacing-lg: 4rem;
    --spacing-xl: 6rem;
    --font-display: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    --font-body: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  main {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-md);
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-turquoise), var(--color-accent-purple));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.375rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Sections */
  .featured-section,
  .case-studies-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .featured-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    position: relative;
  }

  .featured-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-accent-turquoise), transparent);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Featured Project */
  .featured-project {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
      rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.08), 
      rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08)
    );
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .featured-project:hover {
    border-color: rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.15);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-accent-turquoise);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .featured-project h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .project-description {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .project-details {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .project-details h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    color: var(--color-accent-turquoise);
  }

  .project-details ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .project-details li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-details li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-turquoise);
  }

  .project-tech {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .tech-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--color-accent-purple);
  }

  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .project-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .link-github {
    background: var(--color-accent-turquoise);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .link-github:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-purple);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.3);
  }

  .link-docs {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-purple);
    color: var(--color-accent-purple);
  }

  .link-docs:hover {
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1);
  }

  .coming-soon-text {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* Case Studies Grid */
  .case-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .case-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .case-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .case-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-purple);
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .case-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .case-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .status-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .status-planned {
    background: rgba(157, 157, 170, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    border: 1px solid rgba(157, 157, 170, 0.3);
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-accent-purple), transparent);
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-accent-turquoise);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-purple);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.3);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .featured-project {
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .project-links {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .project-links a {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .case-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Focus styles */
  a:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent-turquoise);
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }
</style>
